					alt="Jeanine White at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Studying for my final year of engineering school, I'm deeply interested in the application of machine learning to images and videos and the use of such systems to give computers more knowledge and thus autonomy navigating the real world.
						
					</p>
					<p>
						After 2 years of preparatory school, I've joined Télécom SudParis, one of the best Grande Ecole in Computer Science. I had the opportunity to take courses in various fields such as Mathematics, Computer Science, Project Management, Signal Processing, Information Theory and more.
						I started to gear myself towards image processing and computer vision as soon as the second year. Indeed, as a video editor and a digital art generalist (photography, 3D, videography), those fields sit at the intersection of my personnal and professional interests.
						During my last year of school, I acquired many indispensable tools as Python, C++, Java, CUDA, OpenCV, Tensorflow, Pandas, OpenGL.
						Moreover, I applied those tools to different projects.
